1. Layout Components (The Skeleton)
Ye wo components hain jo har page pe common rahenge.

Sidebar.jsx: Isme navigation links honge.

SidebarItem.jsx: Ek single link (Dashboard, Projects etc.) with icon.

Navbar.jsx: Top bar jahan Search, Notifications, aur User Profile hogi.

NotificationDropdown.jsx: Navbar ke andar jo bell icon click karne pe khulega.

2. Dashboard Overview Components (The Stats)
StatsContainer.jsx: Saare cards ka baap (Wrapper).

StatCard.jsx: Ek single card (e.g., "Active Projects: 5"). Isme hum props pass karenge (title, value, color, icon).

3. AI Requirement Section (The Magic)
Isko alag se todna zaroori hai kyunki isme logic zyada hoga.

RequirementSection.jsx: Wrapper for the input and AI output.

RequirementInput.jsx: Sirf textarea aur "Analyze" button wala part.

AILoader.jsx: Ek mast animation jo dikhayega ki AI soch raha hai (Lottie files use kar sakte ho).

AITaskPreview.jsx: AI ne jo tasks split kiye hain, unki ek list dikhane ke liye.

TaskPill.jsx: AI breakdown ke andar ek single task (e.g., "Setup Auth").

4. Project Tracking Components (The Progress)
ProjectTracker.jsx: Main tracking area.

RoadmapStepper.jsx: Wo dots wali line (Planning -> Dev -> Testing).

StepItem.jsx: Ek single step (Active, Completed, ya Pending state ke saath).

ProgressBar.jsx: Ek horizontal ya circular progress bar component.

5. Data Table Components (The History)
ProjectTable.jsx: Pure table ka structure.

TableHeader.jsx: Table ki heading row.

TableRow.jsx: Ek single project ki row.

StatusBadge.jsx: "In-Progress" (Yellow), "Completed" (Green) wale chote tags.




